        "image": "shopify://shop_images/smartmouth-groupproduct-img.jpg",
        "right_heading": "Oral Health",
        "right_text": "<p>Oral health encompasses the health of the teeth, gums, mouth, throat, and oral cavity. It plays a significant role in your ability to smile, speak clearly, chew, and swallow — and it influences your overall health and quality of life. A <a href=\"https://www.nidcr.nih.gov/research/oralhealthinamerica/section-3a-summary\">substantial percentage</a> of the American population faces oral health challenges with 90 percent of adults experiencing tooth decay and 50 percent dealing with gum disease.</p>",
        "padding_top": 52,
        "padding_bottom": 52
      }
    },
    "faqs_accordion_mKDW7D": {
      "type": "faqs-accordion",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_item_eaMUrW": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How does oral health affect overall health?",
            "content": "<p>Your mouth plays an essential role in your digestive, respiratory, endocrine, nervous, and immune systems, so it’s not surprising that your oral health can affect the general health of your body.</p>\n\n<p>While it’s difficult to pinpoint causation, researchers have linked oral microorganisms with many systemic disorders, including cardiovascular, respiratory, gastrointestinal, and kidney diseases as well as diabetes. Moreover, research suggests gum disease is a risk factor for adverse pregnancy outcomes, including premature labor and delivering a low-weight infant.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_item_JNcLYz": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How to improve oral health…",
            "content": "<div itemprop=\"text\">\n                        \n<p>The following practices can help you maintain optimal oral health:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Eat a <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC8187263/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" onclick=\"javascript:window.open('https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC8187263/', '_blank', 'noopener'); return false;\" data-uw-rm-brl=\"PR\" data-uw-original-href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC8187263/\">healthy diet</a> rich in fruits and vegetables.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>\n<a href=\"/product/smartmouth-premium-zinc-ion-toothpaste-6oz/\" data-uw-rm-brl=\"PR\" data-uw-original-href=\"/product/smartmouth-premium-zinc-ion-toothpaste-6oz/\">Brush your teeth</a> twice a day to remove the buildup of dental plaque, a colorless film of bacteria. Brush for two minutes each time, and make sure you clean all sides of your teeth.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Use dental floss to remove the debris between your teeth at least once a day.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Rinse your mouth daily with an <a href=\"/product/smartmouth-original-activated-mouthwash-16oz/\" data-uw-rm-brl=\"PR\" data-uw-original-href=\"/product/smartmouth-original-activated-mouthwash-16oz/\">alcohol-free rinse</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Avoid using <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC9875717/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" onclick=\"javascript:window.open('https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC9875717/', '_blank', 'noopener'); return false;\" data-uw-rm-brl=\"PR\" data-uw-original-href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC9875717/\">tobacco products</a>, which can negatively affect your dental health.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn how to <a href=\"/oral-health/dry-mouth/\" data-uw-rm-brl=\"PR\" data-uw-original-href=\"/oral-health/dry-mouth/\">prevent dry mouth</a>. Your saliva helps maintain the health of your teeth and gums.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Visit your dentist for regular cleanings and checkups.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"swp-hidden-panel-wrap\" style=\"display: none; visibility: collapse; opacity: 0\"><div class=\"swp_social_panel swp_horizontal_panel swp_flat_fresh  swp_default_full_color swp_individual_full_color swp_other_full_color scale-100  scale-\" data-min-width=\"1100\" data-float-color=\"#ffffff\" data-float=\"none\" data-float-mobile=\"none\" data-transition=\"slide\" data-post-id=\"14197\">\n<div class=\"nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button swp_twitter\" data-network=\"twitter\"><a class=\"nc_tweet swp_share_link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=How+to+improve+oral+health%E2%80%A6&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fhow-to-improve-oral-health%2F\" data-link=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=How+to+improve+oral+health%E2%80%A6&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fhow-to-improve-oral-health%2F\" data-uw-rm-brl=\"PR\" data-uw-original-href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=How+to+improve+oral+health%E2%80%A6&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fhow-to-improve-oral-health%2F\" aria-label=\"twitter - open in a new tab\" data-uw-rm-empty-ctrl=\"\" data-uw-rm-ext-link=\"\" uw-rm-external-link-id=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=how+to+improve+oral+health%e2%80%a6&amp;url=https%3a%2f%2fwww.smartmouth.com%2ffaqs%2fhow-to-improve-oral-health%2f$twitter\"><span class=\"swp_count swp_hide\"><span class=\"iconFiller\"><span class=\"spaceManWilly\"><i class=\"sw swp_twitter_icon\"></i><span class=\"swp_share\">Tweet</span></span></span></span></a></div>\n<div class=\"nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button swp_linkedin\" data-network=\"linkedin\"><a class=\"nc_tweet swp_share_link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fhow-to-improve-oral-health%2F\" data-link=\"https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartmouth.com%2Ffaqs%2Fhow-t